{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2020-11-09-wpf-binding-element-name/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"LAP-TECH"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"689db05a-7694-512e-a16c-78aebb7be8d5","excerpt":"近排寫左個WPF Control, 入面需要用到 ElementName 去做 Source Binding 你會見到係  入面有個 , 而我係  入面就用  去 Reference 番個 , 當  既時候  就會轉為 Red 就咁睇落好似冇咩問題, 行Debug…","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1989a8d6ed1f1962c64da4f26993f134/28be2/cover.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.70270270270271%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Binding\"\n        title=\"Binding\"\n        src=\"/static/1989a8d6ed1f1962c64da4f26993f134/1c72d/cover.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1989a8d6ed1f1962c64da4f26993f134/a80bd/cover.jpg 148w,\n/static/1989a8d6ed1f1962c64da4f26993f134/1c91a/cover.jpg 295w,\n/static/1989a8d6ed1f1962c64da4f26993f134/1c72d/cover.jpg 590w,\n/static/1989a8d6ed1f1962c64da4f26993f134/28be2/cover.jpg 786w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>近排寫左個WPF Control, 入面需要用到 ElementName 去做 Source Binding</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"xml\"><pre class=\"language-xml\"><code class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Style</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">x:</span>Key</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>ButtonStyle<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">TargetType</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>{x:Type Button}<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Setter</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">Property</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Template<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Setter.Value</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n            <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ControlTemplate</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">TargetType</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>{x:Type Button}<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n                <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Border</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">BorderThickness</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>2<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">BorderBrush</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>{TemplateBinding BorderBrush}<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n                    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>TextBox</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">x:</span>Name</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>PART_TextBox<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n                <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>Border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n                <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ControlTemplate.Triggers</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n                    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>DataTrigger</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">Binding</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>{Binding Path=IsFocused, ElementName=PART_TextBox}<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">Value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>True<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n                        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Setter</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">Property</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>BorderBrush<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">Value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Red<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n                    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>DataTrigger</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n                <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ControlTemplate.Triggers</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n            <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ControlTemplate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>Setter.Value</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>Setter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>Style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>你會見到係 <code class=\"language-text\">Border</code> 入面有個 <code class=\"language-text\">TextBox</code>, 而我係 <code class=\"language-text\">DataTrigger</code> 入面就用 <code class=\"language-text\">ElementName</code> 去 Reference 番個 <code class=\"language-text\">TextBox</code>, 當 <code class=\"language-text\">TextBox.IsFocused</code> 既時候 <code class=\"language-text\">Border.BorderBrush</code> 就會轉為 Red</p>\n<p>就咁睇落好似冇咩問題, 行Debug既時候都冇事. 但當我想係用 <code class=\"language-text\">Visibility.Collapse</code> 收埋佢個一刻就出事喇.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">System.Windows.Data Error: 4 : Cannot find source for binding with reference &#39;ElementName=PART_TextBox&#39;. BindingExpression:Path=IsFocused; DataItem=null; target element is &#39;Button&#39; (Name=&#39;&#39;); target property is &#39;NoTarget&#39; (type &#39;Object&#39;)</code></pre></div>\n<p>如果咁寫成單野就冇事</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"xml\"><pre class=\"language-xml\"><code class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Style</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">x:</span>Key</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>ButtonStyle<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">TargetType</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>{x:Type Button}<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Setter</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">Property</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Template<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Setter.Value</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n            <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ControlTemplate</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">TargetType</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>{x:Type Button}<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n                <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Border</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">BorderThickness</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>2<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">BorderBrush</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>{TemplateBinding BorderBrush}<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n                    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>TextBox</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">x:</span>Name</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>PART_TextBox<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n                <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>Border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n                <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ControlTemplate.Triggers</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n                    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!--\n                    &lt;DataTrigger Binding=\"{Binding Path=IsFocused}\" Value=\"True\">\n                        &lt;Setter Property=\"BorderBrush\" Value=\"Red\" />\n                    &lt;/DataTrigger>\n                    --></span>\n                    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Trigger</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">Binding</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>{Binding Path=IsFocused}<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">SourceName</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>PART_TextBox<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">Value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>True<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n                        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Setter</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">Property</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>BorderBrush<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">Value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Red<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n                    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>Trigger</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n                <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ControlTemplate.Triggers</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n            <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ControlTemplate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>Setter.Value</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>Setter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>Style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>見到有咩唔同未? 就係由 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;DataTrigger Binding=&quot;{Binding Path=IsFocused, ElementName=PART_TextBox}&quot;</code> 變成 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Trigger Binding=&quot;{Binding Path=IsFocused}&quot; SourceName=&quot;PART_TextBox&quot;</code></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"寫在WPF Binding ElementName時","date":"November 09, 2020"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2020-11-09-wpf-binding-element-name/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020-10-22-c-sharp-element-at/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"WPF ElementAt 慢過龜"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020-11-16-wpf-datepicker-string/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"WPF DatePicker StringFormat"}}}}}